What is Hello English memory map?
Based on the latest research on the way the human brain learns new stuff, Hello English 'memory map' has been designed to emulate how your brain tends to remember the words and phrases that you have learned in various lessons on Hello English, till date.
The words in the 'Long-term' memory are the ones that you are most likely to remember for months or even years, in 'Medium-term' are the ones that you are likely to remember for a few weeks and the ones in 'Short-term' are those that you will most likely forget in a few days.
The more you encounter the words and phrases the more you are likely to move them from your short term to long-term memory, and if you get these wrong, you are more likely to forget them.
